### Inline Server Action in Server Component (TSX/JSX)

Source: https://github.com/vercel/next.js/blob/canary/docs/01-app/01-getting-started/08-updating-data.mdx

Shows how to inline a Server Action inside a Server Component by placing the 'use server' directive at the top of the function body. Dependencies: the surrounding file must be a Server Component; inputs are typically FormData when used as a form action. Limitation: cannot inline server actions inside Client Components.

```tsx
export default function Page() {
  // Server Action
  async function createPost(formData: FormData) {
    'use server'
    // ...
  }

  return <></>
}
```

```jsx
export default function Page() {
  // Server Action
  async function createPost(formData: FormData) {
    'use server'
    // ...
  }

  return <></>
}
```

